docs.title: Home

docs.text: This is a Scheduler app prototype for viewing patient windows within a study and booking/ viewing appointments. ** THIS IS A PROTOTYPE AND IS USED FOR FEEDBACK AND LEARNING ** To view; Install Node.js Go into terminal in project dir Type “npm install” Wait for packages and dependencies to install (This may take awhile) Type “npm start” -> Open a browser with local host address to view project
